  "detailed_description": "Post-nuclear atmosphere and turn-based combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>EXPLORE AND SURVIVE!<br>An atmospheric open world to explore. Deadly lakes, rotten deserts and dangerous hills! Dark & beautiful hand-drawn flora & fauna. Hand-painted textures.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>TURN-BASED BATTLES! <br>An army of rescued cats and dogs helps your quest on hex based battle maps. Slay stylish roamers and collect the teeth of the mutants in the underground. Mutant teeth - the currency of the wastes. Buy random weapons with game-play changing powers. Thousands of possible combinations.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>LOOT! <br>Boomboxes, cassettes, Grobo beer bottles. Find and collect hidden items to gain the edge in the underground battles.</li></ul><br>Art by Roland Seer, programming by Rain Pohlak.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/530860/extras/8e95632bf07b915e1478089a1daa3b05.avif?t=1668506573\" width=570 height=808 /></span>",
